snippet.title: Hela | World Premiere Trailer
snippet.description:
Hela is a heart-warming open world game for PC & Consoles. It tells the enchanting story of a witch and her familiars—a gang of brave little mice. For ages, the kind witch has used her magic to aid the local folk, but now she has fallen ill and needs help herself. It’s up to the mice to find a cure and keep the “witch business” running in the meantime!

Whishlist now on Steam
